message.body: I hope your weekend went well at the wedding!!
Oh man. I can't believed you remembered. Yeah it was intense and amazing and surreal. I feel like a princess after all that. How's school ? How was your weekend

School is going well for me, I actually have Monday's off. My weekend went really well actually, I ran into a high school friend on the dance floor Saturday late night. I haven't seen her in 10 years, crazy stuff!
I have class at 9 tomorrow :( I would be happy to meet up any time in the afternoon though.
Crazy. Will you be around tomorrow? I have class all day. Want to meet for a Coffee at 10 am?
